1.预定页面请求卡片信息接口

url : http://www.12301.local/route/index.php?c=product_annualCard&a=getCardsForOrder

参数: pid=3026(产品id)
      physics=1111,2222,33333(物理卡号),当这个参数为空的时候表示购买虚拟卡

返回:
{
    "code": 200,
    "data": [
        {
            "virtual_no": "111655",
            "sid": "3385",
            "physics_no": "",
            "card_no": ""
        }
    ],
    "msg": ""
}

2.预定页面请求订单信息接口

url : http://www.12301.local/route/index.php?c=product_annualCard&a=getOrderInfo

参数 : pid=3026(产品id)
       aid=3385(上级供应商id)
       type=virtual|physics(购买的是虚拟卡还是物理卡)

返回:

{
    "code": 200,
    "data": {
        "product": {
            "ltitle" : ""mm--测试景点",
            "title": "优惠票",
            "price": 1, //价格
            "storage": "1" //库存
        },
        "privileges": [ //特权产品
            {
                "tid": "25786",
                "limit_count": "1,2,3",
                "title": "三人票",
                "pid": "22874",
                "ltitle": "九顶塔"
            },
            {
                "tid": "28274",
                "limit_count": "2,3,4",
                "title": "成人票",
                "pid": "25271",
                "ltitle": "测试景区0308003"
            }
        ],
         "pay": {
            "is_self": 0,   //是否自供应
            "remain": 49.63,
            "credit": "6.61"
        },
        "supplier": {   //供应商系想你
            "name": "慢慢的店铺",
            "linkman": "18750178296",
            'intro' : ""
        }
    },
    "msg": ""
}

3.如果购买虚拟卡，订单提交之前需要先请你去这个接口，判断会员是否已经绑定过其他年卡

url : http://www.12301.local/route/index.php?c=product_annualCard&a=isNeedToReplace

参数: mobile=13123196340(手机号)
      name=翁彬(联系人姓名)
      id_card=350181191062332(身份证)
      sid=3385(年卡供应商)

返回:

{
    "code": 200,
    "data": {
        "exist": 1,
        "name": "来自汪星人的神秘年卡",
        "left": "1/20"
    },
    "msg": ""
}



